## Quarto

-   Is an open-source tool for scientific and technical publishing.
-   Creates outputs including PDF, Word, HTML reports, books, websites, presentations & more.
-   Keeps analysis and report together by mixing natural language, code and its outputs.
-   Makes content and structure of a document explicit
-   Plain text facilitates collaboration and reproducible workflows

